original: Ekebohm, Hans David, kontorschef, Göteborg, f. 30/8/90 i Sthlm av sjö-kapt. David E. o. h. h. f. Ramström. G. 26 m. Elsa Schultzberg. Barn: Britta f. 35. — Kont. h. G. A. du Rietz i Sthlm 05-10, olika anst. 10-12, v. Sthlms Diskontobank o. korresp. v. A-B de Lavals Ångturbin 12-14, v. A-B A. Herlitz & C:o i Petersburg 14-17, olika anst. 17-18, anst. v. olika föret. m. verksamih. på Ryssl. 18-25, kassör v. Hallands Ångbåts A-B i Gbg 25-28, kont:chef där sed. 28.
translated: Ekebohm, Hans David, office manager, Gothenburg, b. 30/8/90 in Stockholm to sea captain David E. and his wife Ramström. Married on 26 November 1910 to Elsa Schultzberg. Children: Britta b. 1935. Worked at G. A. du Rietz in Stockholm 1905-1910, various employments 1910-1912, at Stockholm Discount Bank and correspondent for A-B de Lavals Ångturbin 1912-1914, at A-B A. Herlitz & C:o in Petersburg 1914-1917, various employments 1917-1918, employed with various companies with operations in Russia 1918-1925, cashier at Hallands Ångbåts A-B in Gothenburg 1925-1928, appointed office manager there from 1928 onwards.
